rows.label: tev010902_MSG0001
rows.name:
My Aphrodite is a work of art, and I would have given
anything to prevent her from being damaged by the
likes of that rogue![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010902_MSG0002
rows.name:
But alas! Now I won't be able to proceed with my
Outfitters duties for a while.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010902_MSG0003
rows.name:
This crime can never be excused. Gods may forgive,
but my keen sense of aesthetics does not.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010902_MSG0004
rows.name:
Hmmm? Do you need something? Forgive me,
but I'm in no mood for idle chitchat with strangers.
If you have some business with me, it must wait.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev010902_MSG0005
rows.name:
Surely you also have times where you don't feel like
speaking with people?[ST:wait ]
